<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2026-05-31"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03/group03> .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A group ontology that grounds perceived task objects (cups, cutlery, plate, toy blocks, basket) as typed, role-bearing, affordance-carrying individuals, so that an OWL DL reasoner can infer which objects are graspable."@en .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "AI Capstone 2026 - Group 03 Semantic Grounding Ontology"@en .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "g03" .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03/" .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Group 03 submission for Homework 5. Imports the shared course vocabulary, supplies the OWL definition of cap:GraspableObject, and declares the environment instances used to infer graspability."@en .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group03> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "AI Capstone 2026 - Group 03 Semantic Grounding Ontology"@en .
